text: Fluter Agaj (born 24 December 1994) is a Swiss–Kosovan footballer who plays as a defender for FC Schlieren and the Kosovo women's national team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Swiss women's footballers Category:Swiss people of Kosovan descent
